summary: The 3rd in my series of Landscaped Player Homes dresses up the exterior area of the Riften home making it a more welcoming haven. Adds a Chimney, some nautical decor and harvestable nests for the chickens and more.
descriptionHtml:
Number 3 in my Landscaped Player Homes series of mods, Landscaped Honeyside in Riften adds a bit of a nautical flair to the houses\' exterior as well as improved lighting and a bit of additional flora.. Added egg bearing Chicken nests to the garden area and attempted to address the (Vanilla respawn rate of eggs and some crops ) that did not respawn. ( If the Eggs and Leeks respawn, please advise me.
Have not run into any Incompatibility issues with other mods to date.

You can grab the Landscaped Breezehome and Landscaped Proudspire here. [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=8677]Landscaped_Player_Homes_WIP[/url]
author: Ohiogramps
